Northrop Grumman also performs various foreign functions in the [[War on Drugs]]. The company sends planes to spray [[herbicide]]s on suspected [[cocaine]] fields in [[Colombia]] and [[opium]] [[poppy]] fields in [[Afghanistan]].<ref name="maxjourdan">{{cite news
